---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 173
  - Title: Yoga-Vasishtha
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Volition, Obedience and Conformity=Intention
---
The fruits of consummation ripen through patiently following the
injunctions of the Shastras and repeating the mantrams given at the
Initiations without haste for success, and by perfecting oneself
through long practice.
